text: Glenwood Township is a township in Walsh County, North Dakota, United States. 53.5% (114) of the population are male, and the other 46.5% (99) are female.http://www.city-data.com/township/Glenwood-Walsh-ND.html ==References== ==See also== *Walsh County, North Dakota Category:Townships in North Dakota Category:Townships in Walsh County, North Dakota
